originalText.text: Dr. Hosny is a total lifesaver! I struggled with chronic lower back pain for years until meeting with him. His expert care and innovative treatments like laser therapy brought real relief. Thanks to Dr. Hosny, I'm pain free and my quality of life is restored!

originalText.text: Dr. Hosny is very knowledgeable, kind, and reassuring. I’ve rarely met a doctor who clearly cares so much about his patients and treats them like family members. He is overseeing my care for a herniated disc and sciatica, and has been a blessing to work with. The office staff are also amazing and have been very communicative with me and my insurance. Highly recommend this practice to anyone who needs pain management care! Best of luck to you.

originalText.text: Just got home from the procedure. Everyone is the office was so warm, kind and caring. I was a little nervous and my nurse talked me down from my anxiety and it just continued with each person I met. Doctors are both excellent. It was very quick.

originalText.text:
The visit with the Doctor Gupta was easy and clear.  I feel confident that my health is in good hands.  This is quite a contrast from my initial visit when the visit should have been 11:00 and I went to the wrong address and then called the office to be told that it was in Manhattan and not a Brooklyn address where I was.  I was rescheduled for 12:45 and so I quickly regrouped, though in lots of pain, and went to the Manhattan address.  Registered and provided all required information.  At 3:00 I was told by the attendant who did not originally serve me, that the doctor had been in a procedure for a while and so I would have to reschedule.  My attendance today was with great reservations but it turned out to be a success and so I am grateful that I pushed through and attended.

To follow up, yesterday I had my pain relieving procedure.  It just been a day and already I have noticed much difference.  I am looking forward to the future pain free
Days.

originalText.text: I had a good experience with Dr. Gupta for my migraines. I've been to a neurologist and they just gave me medication. I feel like she listened to me and gave me other options to explore to try to find the cause of my migraines. The entire staff was so courteous and friendly. Definitely will be going back to them.
